### Create membership (identity must exist in your app’s identity store)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/memberships
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identityId": "00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001",
  "tenantId": "7566502f-082a-44e1-b95b-3e08cfa5b68b",
  "role": "member"
}

### List memberships for a tenant
GET http://localhost:3000/api/memberships/tenant/7566502f-082a-44e1-b95b-3e08cfa5b68b

### List memberships for an identity
GET http://localhost:3000/api/memberships/identity/00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001

### Get one membership
GET http://localhost:3000/api/memberships/11111111-1111-4111-8111-111111111111

### Update role
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/memberships/11111111-1111-4111-8111-111111111111
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "admin"
}

### Delete membership
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/memberships/11111111-1111-4111-8111-111111111111
